   {:e #blake3 "f2194dab10b6f7e7d682a6d67ffc26e87ba9177dfeb00ec54e5c8e4a21ee36d6" :a :task/description :v "CONTEXT: Each correctness fix requires verification beyond existing tests. This task creates the paired test suite. UNIT TESTS (crates/braid-kernel/src/concept.rs test module): (1) test_find_nearest_no_unwrap_panic — call find_nearest_concept with 0, 1, 3 concepts. Verify no panic in any case (regression guard for DEFECT-002 fix). (2) test_crystallize_centroids_normalized — crystallize 5 similar observations, verify each NewConcept.centroid has L2 norm within 1e-5 of 1.0 (DEFECT-003). (3) test_crystallize_large_cluster_centroid_normalized — crystallize 20 observations into one cluster, verify centroid norm (catches accumulation drift). (4) test_find_nearest_uses_latest_embedding — store two different :concept/embedding assertions for same entity (simulating re-embedding). Verify find_nearest_concept uses the second (latest) embedding (DEFECT-005). (5) test_find_nearest_ignores_retracted — store an Assert then a Retract for a concept embedding. Verify the retracted concept is not found (DEFECT-005 variant). UNIT TESTS (crates/braid-kernel/src/embedding.rs test module): (6) test_cosine_dimension_mismatch_returns_zero — cosine_similarity([1,0], [1,0,0]) returns 0.0 in release (DEFECT-004). (7) test_l2_normalize_is_pub_crate — verify l2_normalize is callable from concept.rs (compile-time check, DEFECT-003 enabler). PROPTEST: (8) For any N observations (3..30) with random embeddings, every NewConcept.centroid from crystallize_concepts has L2 norm in [0.99, 1.01]. E2E ADDITION to scripts/e2e_concept_crystallization.sh: (9) After observations, verify braid observe response does NOT silently lose CCE data — check that :exploration/embedding datom exists for each observation (verify via braid query). FAILURE DIAGNOSTICS: Each test logs embedding vectors (first 5 dims), L2 norms, cosine similarities, and entity IDs for debugging. DEPENDS-ON: FIX-UNWRAP, FIX-NORMALIZE, FIX-STALE, FIX-COSINE, FIX-WRITE-ERR. FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/concept.rs, crates/braid-kernel/src/embedding.rs, scripts/e2e_concept_crystallization.sh" :op :assert}
